item.title: Squash Blossoms Inabraw with Fried Milkfish
item.description: The dish also contains long string beans (sitaw) with its young tops included, saluyot, and broiled milkfish. Inabraw is an Ilocano way of cooking veggie with fermented fish paste (bagoong isda) without any sauteing as opposed to pinakbet. Mangantayon! Now you know how to say bon app√©tit in Iloko
